      "part_of_speech": "noun",
      "meaning": "“马铃薯”的别称，常用于“洋芋”。",
      "examples": [
        "云南人称土豆为‘洋芋’。"
      ],
      "traditional_char": "芋"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "part_of_speech": "noun",
      "meaning": "“甘薯”的别称，常用于“山芋”。",
      "examples": [
